===Pronunciation===
אבק / 'âbaq / aw-bak'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''אבק'''

# Probably to float away (as vapor), but used only as denominative from אבק / 'âbâq {{GG|80}}; to [[bedust]], that is, grapple: - [[wrestle]].

